to install the deb:

0. If this is a fresh install you probably want to mount up the data disk and make sure:
    /opt/atlantis is symlinked to it
    /var/lib/docker is symlinked to it
    /var/log/atlantis is symlinked to it

1. add apt repos for supervisor and docker (replace sv2 with the appropriate region suffix)

sudo sh -c "echo deb [arch=amd64] http://apt.sv2/atlantis-supervisor precise main > /etc/apt/sources.list.d/atlantis-supervisor.list"
sudo sh -c "curl https://get.docker.io/gpg | apt-key add -"
sudo sh -c "echo deb https://get.docker.io/ubuntu docker main > /etc/apt/sources.list.d/docker.list"
sudo apt-get update

2. install atlantis-supervisor

sudo apt-get install -y atlantis-supervisor
